name: d2 anti-aircraft system
description:
The d2 anti-aircraft system is used to counter heavy air strikes and ends the war by targeting the enemy strategic ships.
The d2 system is a hidden weapon inside the ground that in critical situations, according to the command of the ready-to-launch command, its hydrogen missiles are fired into the depths of space in a short time.
In the recent war in Area 51, General Arl fired directly at the energy source of the enemy command ship, repelling and defeating the enemy.
